<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal - Virtual Arbitration &amp; Online Dispute Resolution&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Arbitration/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Sep 18 11:38:53 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
