<h2><A NAME="offsite">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/earth2_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Links to Related Off-Site Resources</h2>
<DL>

<DT><B><A HREF="http://vmag.law.vill.edu:8080/">The Virtual 
Magistrate</A></B>
 <DD>a specialized, on-line arbitration and
   fact-finding system for disputes involving:
     * Users of on-line systems;
     * Those who claim to be harmed by wrongful messages; and
     * System operators (to the extent that complaints or demands for
       remedies are directed at the System Operator).
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.adr.org/">American Arbitration Association</A></B>
</DL>

