<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - Jake Baker, the U. of Michigan, &amp; the FBI&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org, /pub/Legal/Cases/Baker_UMich_case/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Legal/Cases/Baker_UMich_case
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/Baker_UMich_case/
