<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="watson_case.intro"><B>watson_case.intro</B></a>
<DD>summary of what happened in the Dennis Watson case, 
    including what the charges were, on what grounds they were filed, etc.
    Math professor Dennis W. Watson was prosecuted for child pornography 
    crimes, with much media fanfare, after simply accessing certain 
    newsgroups and verifying that they did indeed contain such material, 
    in the process of Watson's work on school computing policies.
</DL>

