<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Legal Cases - Fred Cherry v. Janet Reno (Cherry v. DoJ)&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="FF0000">

