<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Legal Cases - Toys 'R' Us v. Roadkills-R-Us WWW Pages&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD><BODY>

