</TR></TABLE>

<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_trans_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - Toys 'R' Us v. Roadkills-R-Us WWW Pages&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org, /pub/Legal/Cases/Toys_R_Us/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Legal/Cases/Toys_R_Us
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/Toys_R_Us/
</H5>



<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<H1><TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD></H1>
<H1><TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD></H1>
<H1><TD><A HREF="#onsite">On-Site Links</A></TD></H1>
