<DT><a href="online_court.note"><B>online_court.note</B></a>
<DD>In a move to save lawyers time and money, the Quebec
    Court of Appeal announced it will become the first
    judicial body in Canada to allow lawyers to argue motions
    and plead cases using video-conferencing technology.
</DL>

