Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="dos_tcp-ip.faq"><B>dos_tcp-ip.faq</B></a>
<DD>Frequently Asked Questions and Answers about TCP/IP
    (Internet protocols) and DOS.
<DT><a href="gzip123.zip"><B>gzip123.zip</B></a>
<DD>gzip and gunzip for DOS. Allows PC users to directly open 
    and create Unix gnu-zip (.gz) and compress (.Z) files.
<DT><a href="tar.zip"><B>tar.zip</B></a>
<DD>tar for DOS. Allows PC users to directly open and create Unix
    &quot;tape archive&quot; (.tar) files.
</DL>

