<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Driving</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Driving</CENTER></H2>

Drive the slick black dawn<BR>
drive straight<BR>
today, drive smooth today<BR>
clear today<BR>
away<BR>
a way of living<BR>
a way of not giving into the light<BR>
the bright and glittery<BR>
the slithery misery of lies<BR>
and cries behind the reds and the blues <BR>
and the flashy in my eyes<BR>
drive me blind<BR>
fingers lightly on the frets<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
