<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;GII/NII - Telemedicine, Medical Networking &amp;amp; Remote Surgery&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/EFF/Policy/GII_NII_III_NREN_NPN/Telemedicine/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Nov 06 11:26:38 PDT 1996</h6><br>
