<BR><h2><A NAME="files"></a>
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="netgd_hu.zip"><B>netgd_hu.zip</B></a>
<DD>EFF Net Guide, Hungarian version in a ZIP-compressed archive
    for DOS users. Use Codepage 437 to get the proper characters
    (DOES include accents and other diacritic marks.) See Updates/
    subdirectory for updates. Currently at vers. 3.1. This 
    version is split into several files, by chapter since DOS/Win 
    text viewers often cannot view large files. [A Kalauz Magyar valtozatat,
    ASCII, DOS. Ekezetek nelkuli karakterekkel.]
<DT><a href="netguide.hu.gz"><B>netguide.hu.gz</B></a>
<DD>EFF Net Guide, Hungarian version (plain ASCII text, gzip-
    compressed) This version does NOT have accents or other
    diacritic marks. See Updates/ subdirectory for updates.
    Currently at vers. 3.1. [A Kalauz Magyar valtozatat,
    ASCII, UNIX. Ekezetes karakterekkel.]
</DL>

