<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>The part you don't know about our phone conversations</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR = "FFFFFF" TEXT = "000000">

<H2><CENTER>The part you don't know about <BR>our phone 
conversations (Digital romance)</CENTER></H2>

Oval halo of soft white light
<BR>backlights my inner lids
<BR>upon which does play
<BR>the silent movie of my fantasy of you.
<P>
And your beautiful face
<BR>is burned into my soul.
<P>
Fingers play on the soft down clouds
<BR>of pillows.
<BR>imagining in their own
<BR>the texture and structure of your frame
<BR>Though always frustratingly remainingly intangibly. 
<P>
And your luscious silence. 
<BR>Ever my electronic dryad 
<BR>appearing from nowhere and disappearing into the dawn 
<P>
rubbing my eyes, 
<BR>tomorrow alone again.
</BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
