<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

This is a collection of files which, together, form a list of information sources related to the Internet and Computer-Mediated Communication.  Most are in gzipped format.  You can find info on using Internet-CMC below, in plain-text, readable format.

