<BLOCKQUOTE>
<DL>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B>New Mirror Site</B>
    <DD>Sams Publishing has most graciously provided this
    <A HREF = "http://www.mcp.com/sams/libs/cgiscriptarch/Scripts/index.html"
    TARGET = "_parent">Mirror Site</A> 

<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B><A HREF = "jobs.html">Selena Sol's Job Line</A></B>
    <DD>Click here if you are a freelance web programmer and would like 
    to see some of the jobs that came my way which I could not take but 
    felt worthy of your attention.

<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B>Selena Sol in Press</B>
    <DD>Two of my books on CGI 
    Programming are finally on the shelves!  For WAITE
    Group, I have a lengthy chapter in a book called 
    <A HREF = "http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ISBN=157169028X/0225-4303358-453272">CGI 
    How To</A>.  I also have a book from MIS Press 
    called <A HREF = "Book/Mis/toc.html">Instant Web Scripts With CGI</A> 
    is being put online (one chapter per month after October), so feel 
    free to check it out.

    <P>
 
    Also, feel free to check out the little <A HREF = "web_week.html">write 
    up</A> about about my site in Web Week

<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B><A HREF = "http://www.sidestreets.com/info/sssa/" TARGET = "Resource
    Window">Discussion Forum</A></B>
    <DD>The incredible <A HREF = "mailto:webmaster@sidestreets.com">John 
    Cesta</A> has created a beautifully designed discussion board for 
    the script archive.  Here you can discuss installation and setup 
    issues as well as anything else you want related to this site.

<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B><A HREF = "../Personal/Travels/st_croix.html" TARGET = "Resource 
    Window">Travel Log</A></B>
    <DD>Here is a travel log of my recent vacation in St. Croix.

<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B><A HREF = "../Library/Struggle/" TARGET = "Resource Window">The 
     Struggle</A></B>
    <DD>Every month I will try to gather information about a
    struggle in meat space that deserves your attention.  Please take
    some time to read through the material I collect.  And then,
    participate in the struggle for world peace and justice.  It is not
    enough to hide in cyberspace.
<P>

<DT><IMG SRC = "../Graphics/Scripts/redarrow.gif" BORDER = "0">
    <B><A HREF = "http://www.eff.org/cgi-bin/Selena/Mailing_list/mailing_list.cgi"
    TARGET = "Resource Window">Mailing List</A></B>
    <DD>Sign this list to receive infrequent mailings about the status of 
    this page.

</DL>
