<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Net Information &amp; Resources&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Net_info/
</H5>



<br>
   The intent of this directory is to provide recent information resources
   which will help the network novice become familiar with the Internet, 
   including its associated networks, resources, and protocols. This directory
   has been developed in cooperation with the Internet Engineering Task Force
   (IETF) User Documents Working Group. More information about the 
   directory is available in the document access.guide.
<p>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#onsite">On-Site Links</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#offsite">Off-Site Links</A></TD>
</TR></TABLE>


<P></CENTER><BR><HR>
