<DD><A HREF="http://gopher.econ.lsa.umich.edu/">Economics</A> and the
Internet

<DT><B>GENERAL REFERENCE</B>
<DD>The <A HREF="http://www.cnam.fr/Jargon/">Jargon File</A> (a.k.a. 
Hacker's Dictionary) - searchable hypertext WWW version
<DD><A HREF="http://www.access.digex.net/~ikind/babel95a.html">Babel</A>: 
A Glossary of Computer-oriented Abbreviations and Acronyms
