http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Poetry/waste.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040137 text/html 870
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:01:42 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 700
Last-modified: Mon, 22 Jan 1996 19:33:57 GMT
