<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Waste</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Waste</CENTER></H2>

I feel fear<BR>
Lonliness' jear<BR>
are you with him while I sit here<BR>
400 miles away trying not to care?<BR>
<P>
A tear<BR>
as you clear your conscience<BR>
and I hear you say<BR>
that you're not ready though you love me.<BR>
<P>
The searing pain of physical acceptance<BR>
tearing myself apart because I know what I'm doing<BR>
is wearing feelings that are not mine<BR>
when my soul beckons for me to hear its wisdom<BR>
a mere realization that happiness is all that is dear<BR>
<P>
and all this even though<BR>
I know you're asleep<BR>
at home<BR>
missing me, and kissing me<BR>
in your dreams.<BR>

</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
