<DOCNO>WT10-B05-170</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000241-B004-18</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Prose/emerge1.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040447 text/html 4798
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:04:51 GMT
