<P></CENTER><BR><HR>
<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="ca_sb1115_92_cec.amend"><B>ca_sb1115_92_cec.amend</B></a>
<DD>1992 amendment to the Calif. Education Code
    forbidding even private institutions from taking disciplinary measures
    against students' speech and expression. For once an 
    *anti*-censorship regulation.
</DL>

