<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Library/Struggle/sayon.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040925 text/html 3513
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:09:28 GMT
