Reports</A> by State Gopher Server 
<DD><A 
HREF="gopher://spinaltap.micro.umn.edu:70/00Weather/Washington_DC/Washington%20DC"> Washington DC</A> Weather Reports Gopher Server
<DD>Recent <A HREF="gopher://geophys.washington.edu:79/0earthquake"> 
Earthquakes</A> Gopher Server 
<DD>WWW Resume Server: <A HREF="http://ibd.ar.com/Resume/"> View Resumes</A>
<DD>WWW Resume Server: <A HREF="http://ibd.ar.com/Resume-FAQ.html"> Submit 
Resume</A>
</DL>

<br><hr><br>
<a href="mailto:webmaster@eff.org">webmaster@eff.org</a>
