<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Quotables/vote.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040509 text/html 11492
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:05:13 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 11320
Last-modified: Wed, 25 Sep 1996 20:11:57 GMT
