<DL>
<DT><a href="fvpca_93_nz.bill"><B>fvpca_93_nz.bill</B></a>
<DD>Films, Videos &amp; Publications Classification Act of 1993.
<DT><a href="gfiles_legislation.alert"><B>gfiles_legislation.alert</B></a>
<DD>Here's an interesting article from a news
    paper about some kids who made bombs from
    the old `how to make a bomb' files. One MP is
    about to introduce a bill to make possession of
    these files (which would cover historically
    significant documents such as Phrack) illegal. 
    March 1994
<DT><a href="tcra_94_nz.bill"><B>tcra_94_nz.bill</B></a>
<DD>Technology and Crimes Reform bill, sponsored by the
    detested and censorious MP Trevor Rogers, noted for his inflammatory
    verbal attacks on Internetworking.
</DL>

