    scheme, its effects on US competitiveness, the key escrow agents, among 
    others.
<DT><a href="masterkey_clipper.story"><B>masterkey_clipper.story</B></a>
<DD>File containing a fictional story by an 
    anonymous author entitled &quot;Master Key: A Clipper Story.&quot; It is an 
    account of how, after nation-wide implementation of the Clipper Chip, one 
    man breaks the encryption algorithm.
