<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Thinking</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Thinking</CENTER></H2>
No soul<BR>
no feel<BR>
no smile<BR>
surreal
<P>

daydream<BR>
fantasy<BR>
on the rim<BR>
dim<BR>
border of insanity<P>
must not think<BR>
must write<BR>
mumble through the night<P>

remember not to<BR>
remember not to<BR>
calm<BR>
relax<BR>
numb<BR>
stay numb<BR>
don't think<BR>
whatever else<BR>
never think.<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
